00:18:28,291 --> 00:18:30,541
[Okuru] These medicinal herbs
will help your wounds.

257
00:18:30,625 --> 00:18:33,583
If you leave them on for
a while, it'll feel better.

258
00:18:33,666 --> 00:18:34,875
[Fuu] Thank you.

259
00:18:34,958 --> 00:18:37,625
[Okuru] The forest can be
dangerous at night,

260
00:18:37,708 --> 00:18:40,000
feel free to sleep here.

261
00:18:41,166 --> 00:18:44,875
Uh, my name is Fuu.

262
00:18:44,958 --> 00:18:46,500
What about you?

263
00:18:46,583 --> 00:18:48,125
What's your name?

264
00:18:49,125 --> 00:18:51,666
You can call me Okuru.

265
00:18:54,541 --> 00:18:56,500
[Fuu] Is this where you live?

266
00:18:56,583 --> 00:18:58,458
[Okuru] For the time being.

267
00:18:58,541 --> 00:19:00,166
I'm on a journey.

268
00:19:01,208 --> 00:19:03,666
[Fuu] Have you
been traveling alone?

269
00:19:03,750 --> 00:19:05,000
[Okuru] Yes.

270
00:19:05,083 --> 00:19:07,166
[Fuu] I'm all alone, too.

271
00:19:07,250 --> 00:19:10,041
Those two jerks are gone now.

272
00:19:10,125 --> 00:19:11,500
[Okuru] Two jerks?

273
00:19:11,583 --> 00:19:13,000
[Fuu] Yeah, up until today,

274
00:19:13,083 --> 00:19:14,958
I had a couple
of useless bodyguards

275
00:19:15,041 --> 00:19:17,041
who were traveling with me.

276
00:19:17,125 --> 00:19:19,833
Well, I guess
it doesn't matter now.

277
00:19:21,541 --> 00:19:24,000
Now I don't have anyone
in the whole world.

278
00:19:24,083 --> 00:19:27,666
It doesn't matter if I wind up
dead in a ditch somewhere.

279
00:19:27,750 --> 00:19:31,333
But for some reason, I always
hated the thought of drowning.

280
00:19:31,416 --> 00:19:34,916
I mean your body bloats up
to twice its size, right?

281
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:36,583
Forget that!

282
00:19:36,666 --> 00:19:39,208
I want my corpse
to be beautiful.

283
00:19:40,791 --> 00:19:42,125
[Okuru] In my village,

284
00:19:42,208 --> 00:19:45,583
ever person living there
was taken by the Roaming God.

285
00:19:48,291 --> 00:19:50,041
It's a disease.

286
00:19:50,125 --> 00:19:51,916
Killed every
single one of them.

287
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:54,083
Wiped out the entire village.

288
00:19:57,250 --> 00:20:01,416
I had gone away on a journey,
so I was the only survivor.

289
00:20:01,500 --> 00:20:04,500
I had a family, a wife
and newborn daughter.

290
00:20:04,583 --> 00:20:06,958
They were both taken
by the gods.

291
00:20:08,791 --> 00:20:11,375
I'm sorry.

292
00:20:11,458 --> 00:20:13,791
Death leaves
no beautiful corpses.

293
00:20:13,875 --> 00:20:15,291
None.

294
00:20:36,875 --> 00:20:38,250
Good riddance to those two.

295
00:20:38,333 --> 00:20:39,916
Screw 'em both.

296
00:20:45,083 --> 00:20:46,791
That little bitch.

297
00:20:49,291 --> 00:20:51,291
[Fuu] Where will you
go from here?

298
00:20:51,375 --> 00:20:54,166
[Okuru] I've been
working my way west.

299
00:20:54,250 --> 00:20:56,416
[Fuu] West, huh?

300
00:20:56,500 --> 00:20:59,208
[Okuru] I can't stick
around here much longer.

301
00:20:59,291 --> 00:21:01,375
[Fuu] I've been traveling
in the same direction.

302
00:21:01,458 --> 00:21:04,041
West to Nagasaki.

303
00:21:04,125 --> 00:21:06,125
You see,
I'm looking for a samurai

304
00:21:06,208 --> 00:21:07,916
who smells of sunflowers.

305
00:21:09,166 --> 00:21:10,458
Okuru,

306
00:21:10,541 --> 00:21:14,000
I was thinking,
could I travel with you?

307
00:21:19,958 --> 00:21:22,083
When you're done
sneakin' around, come on out.

308
00:21:22,166 --> 00:21:24,833
I'll take you guys on
whenever you're ready.

309
00:21:28,083 --> 00:21:29,166
[Policeman] We're
police officers with

310
00:21:29,250 --> 00:21:31,250
the Matsumae domain
magistrate's office.

311
00:21:31,333 --> 00:21:33,166
Come along peacefully, Okuru.

312
00:21:33,250 --> 00:21:34,791
Huh?

313
00:21:34,875 --> 00:21:36,541
[Policeman] Give yourself up!

314
00:21:41,750 --> 00:21:46,708
<i>♪ End Theme ♪</i>

